hit me a mail if you like my app.
***********************************************

FlashLite is a simple android app that turns the screen of devices white to serve as a flash/torch light in the dark.
 

Features:
*********
 i.  turns screen white
 ii. runs on android 2.1 and above

Future updates:
***************
 - easy adjustment of brightness level
 - background music.
